welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Biak, Indonesia! Get ready to immerse yourself in the natural beauty of this tropical paradise, known for its pristine beaches, vibrant coral reefs, and rich cultural heritage. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Biak has to offer during your stay."
